Sam Lasky.title: Treasure Trove
Sam Lasky.about:
This is a 14-track collection of songs that I wrote for FAWM, an annual songwriting challenge and community that takes place exclusively on February each year; this is my first FAWM I've ever participated in, and it was an exciting and interesting endeavor to undertake!
These tracks range from house music, electronica, and drum n' bass to genres like jazz-funk, industrial dance, and a brief dip into progressive rock at one point; I hope you enjoy what I worked hard to create this month. : )
Sam Lasky.credits:
released February 26, 2026
lastkeymusic: composition, production, arrangement, album art
